column2: You can’t travel but you can dream! Ask your teen these questions.
Where do you want to travel? How long will you be away? What will you pack? What will you do? What will you see?
Look at a map together if you have one.
Choose a country that they’ve never heard of and look it up together online.",,,,,,,,,,,,,,,1feb242b-3fcb-41e0-879e-5810cee05181,,execute_actions,;
